<paragraph id="IFRS15_BC60"><paranum>BC60</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 15"/><data name="paranum" value="BC60"/></prolog><body><variant id="IFRS15_BC60_V2" base="F58849918"> <p id="IFRS15_P2197">The boards also excluded from the scope of IFRS 15 three types of contracts with customers that they are addressing in other Standards:</p> <ol id="IFRS15_L0166" base="F58849919" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS15_P2198" base="F58849921">leases;</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IFRS15_P2199" base="F58849923">insurance contracts;<xref keyref="footnotes/IFRS15_FN0016" type="fn"/> and</p></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p id="IFRS15_P2200" base="F58849925">financial instruments and other contractual rights or obligations within the scope of the boards&#x2019; other Standards.</p></li></ol></variant></body></paragraph>